Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.82,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:9989,13826}I can feel the sunshine on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:13826,17121}I think I'll bask in it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:22.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:18122,22126}It's a beginning of a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.46,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25338,28466}That's the moment I like the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.51,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29342,33513}the one that starts it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:33513,36849}Something lovely is about to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.72,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:36849,40728}I just have a hunch like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.40,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:40728,48403}Woom! My reflection the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.28,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:48403,52282}Woom! Looks rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:56.03,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:52282,56035}It feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:02.87,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56035,62875}I reach out to the clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:10.67,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:63793,70675}I'm so excited and filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:15.09,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:71467,75096}Love, work, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:57.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112592,117639}Excuse me, aren't you Emi Honma,\Nthe teenage idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:01.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118097,121017}Yes. Have we met somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:03.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121017,123519}I see your picture in the magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:05.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123519,125021}I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:08.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125021,128107}What brings you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:13.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129359,133571}You don't have to say if it puts\Nsomeone in a difficult situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:17.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134238,137533}No, I want to tell you.\NThe truth is, I have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:22.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138326,142997}I've been dating someone, but no one,\Nnot even my management agency, knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:29.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143456,149379}I put a picture taken of us together\Nin my locket and always kept it near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:33.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149379,153049}Once, when I left it in\Nmy dressing room for a moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:37.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153049,157970}Mr. Iwasaki from a rival\Nproduction came and stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:38.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157970,158930}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:43.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159681,163768}And then Mr. Iwasaki came\Nto me and said:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:49.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165228,169399}Let me see, what should I do\Nabout this, this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171693,174070}The press would go crazy\Nif I sold it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:57.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174696,177782}But that would mean\Nthe end of your career.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:02:59.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177782,179909}Please, give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179826,182286}Okay, I'll give it back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:05.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182286,185748}In exchange, your part\Nas Yoko in that new movie,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:10.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185748,190002}you could turn down the part\Nand give it to one of my girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:13.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190628,193589}You could pretend to be sick\Nor something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:17.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193589,197385}If you don't do it, I won't be\Nresponsible for this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200263,201639}How terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:24.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201639,204183}I don't want to cause trouble\Nfor my agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:27.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204183,207478}I came here because\NI don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:32.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207478,212150}Please cheer up.\NI'm sure God will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.90,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:214277,216904}Save the Pretty Idol Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221451,223161}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224620,226164}Big news, big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227123,228166}Sawatari.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229333,231836}The shampoo company's\Nimage girl contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:54.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231836,234130}Look, you passed\Nthe preliminaries! See?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:59.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237175,239594}Wow! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:06.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241596,246058}Yep, you're one step closer\Nto becoming a big star.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246184,247977}This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247977,250188}You'll go to the contest, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250188,251314}Just hold on there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:16.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251981,256527}And when you become a big star,\Ndon't forget about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:17.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256527,257445}Listen…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:22.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257445,262909}No way! She'll be so busy, she won't\Neven be able to come to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:23.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262909,263910}Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:25.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263910,265244}Sawatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:29.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266287,269707}If you think becoming a big star\Nis that easy, you're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:37.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274420,277089}What's with him? Spoilsport.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277089,278925}Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279509,282553}I wonder, was it something we said?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:45.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282553,285890}I don't think so, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:49.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286224,289602}Oh, I almost forgot.\NRina also passed. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:52.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289977,292104}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:56.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294607,296609}I'm pretty sure she entered herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297443,299612}She has a lot\Nof confidence in herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:07.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304283,307662}I'm not going to participate\Nin the contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:08.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307662,308955}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:13.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308955,313960}Now, Meimi, listen. That girl Emi\Nwho came here yesterday for help…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:16.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313960,316629}The one who wants her locket?\NI'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:22.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316838,322510}You don't understand. Emi is one\Nof the judges for that contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:25.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322510,325096}She was one of the past winners.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:29.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325471,329141}And that Mr. Iwasaki is\Nalso one of the judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:33.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329141,333396}Unless Emi announces she is turning\Ndown the role by that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:37.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333396,337358}he says he'll publicize\Nthe picture after the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:44.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337358,344490}I think our best bet would be to get the locket\Nduring the contest and return it to Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:47.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344866,347952}But why do I have\Nto enter a contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:52.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350037,352248}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:56.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352248,356752}I would never have guessed that\Nyou were so afraid of contests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:58.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356752,358170}Just hold on there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:01.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358170,361632}Forget it. Just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:06.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361632,366429}Who says I'm afraid? All right then,\NI'll show you. I'll enter that contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:09.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368264,369599}Forgive me, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:20.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376981,380484}I didn't mean to say what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388326,389535}A note!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:35.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391954,395625}"On the day of the beauty contest,\NI'll take a locket
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:40.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395625,400504}from Mr. Iwasaki of the Rainbow\NProduction Company. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:43.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402673,403507}Hey, come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:54.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413935,414977}Takamiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415728,417146}Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:59.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417146,419440}Did you hear?\NI'm entering that contest too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:02.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420232,422443}I want to test my capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:06.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422860,426572}The one Sawatari was talking about,\Nyou're in it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:08.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426572,428407}Will you come and watch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:12.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428950,432662}Why do I have to go?\NGirls are a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:15.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432662,435873}Oh, all right. Now give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:19.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435873,439335}That's all you think about, St. Tail!\NIt was a man dressed like a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:27.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443422,447802}There's a future star\Nstanding right in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449720,451806}Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:38.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455935,458729}Asuka Jr., have you,\Nyou know, gotten taller?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460022,461649}{\i1}I'd better make my move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:44.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461649,464694}{\i1}Soon the other girls\Nwill start noticing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:52.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468531,472118}{\i1}I'd better stake my claim on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:01.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478749,481043}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:04.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481460,484088}– Hi there!\N– Hi, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:07.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484088,487675}Emi Honma's being\Ninterviewed on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487675,488509}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:12.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488926,492138}{\i1}Emi, congratulations\Non getting the role of Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:17.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492138,497018}{\i1}Thank you.\NI owe everything to all my fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:21.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497018,501355}{\i1}And does that include\Nyour boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:25.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501355,505985}{\i1}My boyfriend is all of my fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506694,508946}{\i1}Poor Emi, it must be hard for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:33.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509739,513451}She's right. She's too young\Nto have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513451,515327}I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:39.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515327,519874}Even junior high kids have\Nsignificant others these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:43.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519874,523919}Meimi, you don't have a boyfriend, do you?\NYou're much too young.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:51.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527590,531343}I never imagined!\NMy Meimi's got a boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:52.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531635,532595}I what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:55.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532595,535765}Oh, dear, my idyllic life\Nis coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:09:00.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535765,540811}Calm down, dear. Meimi hasn't said\Nanything about liking a certain boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:03.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541187,543647}What? You don't like boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:06.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543647,546817}Does that mean you prefer girls?\NThat is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547359,549320}Let's have a heart-to-heart talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:11.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549320,551822}I'm going to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:12.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551822,552948}Enough of this nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552948,554283}But, Eimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:23.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561373,563459}I'm home, Ruby. Did you miss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:28.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565252,568047}You're my best friend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:36.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573761,576180}Sorry. I had something on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:43.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579225,583813}If I become a star,\NI wonder if he'll look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592571,595157}We've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595157,597660}My name is Yamashiro.\NI'm in charge of this contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:01.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598494,601831}This is Mr. Iwasaki\Nfrom Rainbow Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:02.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601831,602665}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:06.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602665,606627}You'd better arrest that burglar.\NShe's such a nuisance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:08.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607002,608629}I'm doing my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:14.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610047,614093}Your father may be a detective,\Nbut how will you arrest her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:19.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614301,619348}Judging from this building's floor\Nplan and her mode of operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:24.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619348,624228}there's a high possibility\Nshe'll appear directly on-stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:28.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624228,628566}And so I thought we could rig\Nthe stage curtain
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:32.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628566,632528}to fall on her like a casting net,\Nthus trapping her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633028,635030}I understand.\NYou have my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:39.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635698,639493}{\i1}I will capture her.\NI won't fail this time.
Comment: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:42.99,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:642997,642997}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:48.00,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:648002,648002}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:55.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652840,655426}And now the contest begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:59.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655843,659555}First is a question-and-answer\Nsegment, then a camera test.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:01.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659555,661140}Entry 1, please come forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:06.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663642,666145}Entry 1, Manami Yoshizawa.\NI'm 16 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:09.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666687,669064}What are you currently\Nmost devoted to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669064,671066}To my music and dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:15.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671066,675487}I am also serious about putting\Nevery effort into this audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:16.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675487,676572}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:20.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676572,680117}– What are your dreams for the future?\N– To become an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:23.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680618,683329}– Please turn to the right.\N– Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:27.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683329,687082}All right.\NNow turn around and smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687333,689919}Make a complete turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689919,691462}That's fine, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691462,693297}This isn't easy, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:35.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693297,695549}Next contestant, entry 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:39.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696842,699595}My name is Mutsumi Hijiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:42.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700638,702598}My name is Yoko Hizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703557,705976}My name is Yuki Uchida.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:48.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705976,708395}Hey, Mimori…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708395,710022}Where's Takamiya and Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710564,712524}I'm sure they'll be out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:53.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712816,713901}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713901,715903}Entry 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:59.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716737,719114}My name is Rina Takamiya.\NI'm 14 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719114,720699}I'm pleased to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:03.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720699,723744}15, is there someone special\Nin your life now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725621,727248}Yes, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:17.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733379,737216}All right, smile.\NNow turn to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:23.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737216,743180}{\i1}Darn that St. Tail. Why does she\Nwant the locket Mr. Iwasaki has?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743180,744640}{\i1}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:30.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746058,750938}{\i1}Never mind. I've got to concentrate\Non capturing her, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:33.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750938,753107}{\i1}All right, come on, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:34.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753399,754608}Look, it's Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:39.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756944,759071}Number 18.\NMy name is Meimi Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:42.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760030,762116}How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:45.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762116,765536}Oh, I'm sorry. I'm 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:49.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765869,769039}What is your idea\Nof the perfect man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769373,771041}This I've got to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:02.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780676,782428}Someone like my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:06.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784430,786015}Rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:09.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787308,789059}Oops, I think I goofed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:18.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792646,798444}And that concludes\Nour program for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:22.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798819,802740}The results of today's judging\Nof these 50 contestants
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:24.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802740,804658}will be sent out within 3 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804658,806952}There's still one left, 51!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:29.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808370,809913}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810205,811915}This part of the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814418,815878}What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:38.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816128,818172}Is there someone left?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:40.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818172,820507}No, I'm sure there were only 50 girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820758,822468}Turn on the lights!\NWhere are the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:51.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827639,831769}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832853,834229}On the screen…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834563,836732}{\i1}St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841445,842738}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:06.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844948,846408}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:10.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848327,850662}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869098,870224}It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875145,876230}Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880984,882694}What is this smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:45.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882986,885197}Is it St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:48.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885406,888826}{\i1}Meimi, I pray God is with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:51.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888826,891662}Now, drop the curtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:55.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893747,895124}Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:15:00.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895999,900254}We'd better not move around now.\NBesides, you seem pretty slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900254,901588}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:05.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902339,905050}Don't worry, you'll be safe with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:17.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911098,917020}What's so funny?\NI haven't told any jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:20.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917479,920482}Drop the curtain! Hurry!\NWhat's the holdup?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:24.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920941,924945}Sorry, Asuka Jr.! We can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925279,927948}Number 51, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928198,930909}I am a thief! How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:33.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931535,933370}Damn! You're not getting the locket!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:37.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934746,937374}I see you, Mr. Iwasaki!\NYou won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:43.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942504,943881}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945215,947259}Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:50.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948886,950220}Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:03.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960314,963984}Beauty contests are fun\Nbut how's this shampoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:08.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965819,968655}Now, watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972284,973494}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:15.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974453,975621}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976330,977289}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988425,990636}St. Tail, that's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:45.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003774,1005150}{\i1}My locket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:50.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007861,1010030}I have the locket!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011865,1013033}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:55.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013200,1015160}Damn this smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:58.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015160,1018497}I'm definitely going\Nto get that St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:07.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022918,1027339}You should be ashamed.\NAs the Mayor's niece, I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:08.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027339,1028966}We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:13.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029633,1033011}Rats. You're not\Ngetting away with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:16.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033554,1036431}I don't care who does it,\Njust pull the rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:17.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036890,1037849}Rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:32.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050821,1052489}– Asuka Jr.!\N– Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052489,1053574}{\i1}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055075,1056743}{\i1}It's so heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:40.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057786,1060539}{\i1}Hurry. I've got to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063458,1065836}This isn't exactly going as I planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066920,1068422}{\i1}This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068880,1070882}I've got you at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074219,1075679}{\i1}He'll hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:01.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078890,1081101}Let me see your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081101,1083270}{\i1}Please don't hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084855,1086815}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:11.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087399,1091778}Asuka Jr.! Sorry! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:20.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095866,1100245}Don't arrest her!\NShe got my locket back for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117387,1118764}{\i1}Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:48.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126063,1128774}She got my locket back for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130108,1131526}{\i1}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140035,1142913}It's a sure bet that I didn't pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:07.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142913,1147376}You can never tell! Sometimes\Nthey go for things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:09.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147959,1149586}– Seira.\N– Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149586,1150462}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:13.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150462,1153090}I can't wait for the results!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:17.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153090,1157844}Don't worry about it.\NYou had the best response!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:24.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162808,1164810}I goofed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:36.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173610,1176446}Give it up, trying to be a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:37.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177030,1177906}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:40.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178657,1180450}Your father wouldn't approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:46.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183078,1186081}If I were your father, I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:54.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192504,1194172}Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:05.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200387,1205809}What a disappointment!\NBoth Meimi and Rina didn't pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:11.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205976,1211273}We thought they'd be able to\Nintroduce us to some handsome actors!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:15.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213692,1215694}Listen here…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:30.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225662,1230083}{\i1}I'm positive he had her\Ntrapped back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:32.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230083,1232169}{\i1}But he let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237048,1238592}{\i1}I'm positive of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:47.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241762,1247476}{\i1}I've got a great idea.\NI'll keep St. Tail away from him.
